metadata.name: E N L U X | 01
metadata.description:
E N L U X | 01 by Balazs Busznyak

A cultivated collection of 7 photographs. Illustrated around a sense of clarity and understanding.

Each piece is 1:1 and holders will receive a physical copy of the print. 

95% of the proceeds will benefit children and families living in remote regions of the Himalayas. Holders will also be provided with the opportunity to visit Zanskar Valley with Enlightened Global. 

Do not dwell in the past. Do not dream of the future. Concentrate the mind on the present moment.
